Package fr.lipn.nlptools.uima.common

Class Summary
BasicPositionedTextTokenIterator This class implements GenericTokenIterator over PositionedText elements.
BasicTokenIterator This class does not add anything to a simple FSIterator over Token types.
BasicTokenPOSLemmaIterator Implements TokenPOSLemmaIterator using LIPN standard types.
DocumentTextFileWriterCasConsumerAE CAS Consumer component (actually in the AE style), which simply writes the document text contained in a view to a text file.
FSIteratorFactory Library about manipulating FSIterator objets.
GenericTokenIterator<T> Generic token iterator abstract class: provides the basic behaviour to iterate over tokens (possibly depending on iterating over sentences).
LipnExternalProgramGenericAnnotator This class is intended to be a super-class for all LIPN componants built using an encapsulated external program.
POSLemmaPairInterpretationTokenPOSLemmaIterator this class extends BasicTokenPOSLemmaIterator for the particular case where POSLemmaPairInterpretation types are expected.
ThreadSafeFSIterator This class implements a thread-safe FSIterator.
TokenByLineCasConsumerAE CAS Consumer component (actually in the AE style), which writes a 'token by line' output.
TokenByLineCollectionReader A collection reader that reads 'token by line' formatted documents from a directory in the filesystem.
TokenByLineWriterFeeder  
TokenPOSLemmaIterator This generic abstract class implements the GenericTokenIterator class for iterating over 3-sized String arrays, each containing the token and its corresponding POS and Lemma annotations.
